\c 12
\s Jobho anozvidavirira
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jobho wakapindura ndokuti:
\p
\v 2 Nokuti zvirokwazvo muri vanhu, uye uchenjeri huchafa nemwi.
\v 3 Asi ndine moyo semwi; handisi mudiki kwamuri. Zvino ndiyani kwaari kusina zvakadai?
\v 4 Ndiri ari chiseko kushamwari yake, anodana kuna Mwari achimupindura; asina mhosva; wakarurama chiseko.
\v 5 Mwenje unozvidzwa mumirangariro yewakachengetedzeka, wakagadzirira vaya vanotedzemuka netsoka.
\v 6 Matende emakororo ane rugare, uye vanotsamwisa Mwari vakachengetedzeka, uyo muruoko rwake Mwari anouisa.
\p
\v 7 Asi bvunzai henyu mhuka, zvino dzichakudzidzisai, neshiri dzematenga, zvino dzichakuudzai.
\v 8 Kana taurai kunyika, zvino ichakudzidzisai; nehove dzegungwa dzichakurondedzerai.
\v 9 Ndiani asingazivi pazvinhu izvi zvese kuti ruoko rwaJehovha rwakaita izvi?
\v 10 Uyo muruoko rwake mune upenyu hwechipenyu chimwe nechimwe, nemweya wenyama yese yemunhu.
\p
\v 11 Nzeve haiidzi mashoko, semukanwa unoravira zvekudya here?
\v 12 Kuvatana kune uchenjeri, ne\add pa\add*kureba kwemazuva pane kunzwisisa.
\v 13 Kwaari kune uchenjeri nesimba, ane zano nekunzwisisa.
\v 14 Tarirai, anokoromora, uye hapangavakwi\add zve\add*; anopfigira munhu, uye hapangazarurwi.
\v 15 Tarirai, anodzivisa dzimvura idzo ndokupwa; uye anodzituma, idzo ndokupidigura nyika.
\v 16 Kwaari kune simba neuchenjeri; wakanyengerwa uye munyengeri ndevake.
\v 17 Anoendesa vapi vemazano vapambiwa, agoita vatongi vave mapenzi.
\v 18 Anosunungura chisungo chemadzimambo, ndokusunga bhanhire pazviuno zvavo.
\v 19 Anoendesa vashumiri vakapambiwa, uye vakasimba ano\add va\add*wisa.
\v 20 Anokamura mashoko evakatendeka, nekubvisa kunzwisisa kwevakura.
\v 21 Anodurura kushora pamusoro pemachinda, nekutembenudza bhanhire revane simba.
\v 22 Anofukura zvinhu zvakadzika kubva parima, uye anobudisira kuchiedza mumvuri werufu.
\v 23 Anokurisa marudzi, ndokuaparadza, awanza marudzi, ndokuabvisa.
\v 24 Anobvisa moyo wemisoro yevanhu venyika, ndokuvadzungairisa murenje musina nzira.
\v 25 Vanotsvangadzira murima uye vasina chiedza, anovadzedzeresa sechidhakwa.